1. *Junak* je hrabro stao u odbranu svoje zemlje. (The hero bravely stood up in defense of his country.)
2. *Junaci* su se borili protiv neprijatelja danima. (The heroes fought against the enemy for days.)
3. Svi vole da slušaju priče o *junacima*. (Everyone likes to hear stories about heroes.)
4. On je pravi *junak* u našim očima. (He is a true hero in our eyes.)
5. Naš *junak* je pobedio u velikoj bitki. (Our hero won a great battle.)
6. *Junaka* su slavili kao heroja nakon što je spasao život deteta. (The hero was celebrated as a hero after saving a child's life.)
7. U ovoj priči, glavni lik se pretvara u *junaka* da bi spasio princezu. (In this story, the main character becomes a hero to save the princess.)
8. *Junaci* su bili hrabri i nisu se plašili da se suoče sa smrću. (The heroes were brave and were not afraid to face death.)
9. *Junaku* su dodelili medalju za hrabrost. (The hero was awarded a medal for bravery.)
10. U ovom filmu, *junak* pokušava da spasi grad od uništenja. (In this movie, the hero tries to save the city from destruction.)

Note: In Serbian language, the word "junak" has a male gender, and the plural form is "junaci".